Subject: [PATCH 2/2] components/linux.bst: Remove redundant LEDS_CLASS_FLASH
 module

The LEDS_CLASS_FLASH module is redundantly inside the PinePhone Pro
group because this was already added inside 98e7e2b67e according to the
git blame command:
- git blame -L 2017,2017 files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh
---
 files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh b/files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh
index eee335cd1..2fc4e94e6 100644
--- a/files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh
+++ b/files/linux/fdsdk-config.sh
@@ -36,7 +36,6 @@ case "$arch" in
 
         module DRM_PANEL_HIMAX_HX8394
 
-        module LEDS_CLASS_FLASH
         module LEDS_SGM3140
     ;;
 esac
